reviewText: i been watching this beautifuly made drama on you tube three times..had to buy it....and have not stop watching this fantastic movies had neighbors drop by to see it as well..the cast better then the american actors...the new girl played the part very good .

This is the most mean-spirited drama I have ever seen. it's one redeeming feature is the eye candy. There is lots of that. Only
Kim Seung Ho seemed to be having any fun. Made me want to see 49 Days again.
I received this DVD as scheduled.  I enjoyed this drama and was happy with the English translation.
